  29 Dec 2004; Daniel Goller <morfic@gentoo.org> lcms-1.13.ebuild:
  Adding elibtoolize

  01 Dec 2004; Mamoru KOMACHI <usata@gentoo.org> lcms-1.12.ebuild,
  lcms-1.13.ebuild:
  Fixed compilation on ppc-macos (Mac OS X doesn't have automake-1.7, so
  autoreconf breaks build on ppc-macos). This closes bug #65618.

  31 Oct 2004; Kito <kito@gentoo.org> lcms-1.12.ebuild, lcms-1.13.ebuild:
  added ~ppc-macos

